{"tid":539653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完呂秉權呢篇野，浸大停學決定真係混亂到不堪","createTime":"2018-01-24T17:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T19:38:11.000Z","uid":36901,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd653b769e832f872e8ef154260fb53ff1608c5","tid":539653,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:45:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/luipingkuen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fluipingkuen%2F&d=JUxhlXtb23yvPGjahr8VzCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5f5ebf9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/luipingkuen/</a><br />\n本人並不贊同浸大學生在語文中心的抗爭手法，對事件和校方對有關同學停學的決定有以下看法：<br />\n<br />\n1. 學生如有錯一定要承認，並應對有關老師及公眾真誠道歉。<br />\n<br />\n2. 學生如被證實有錯，校方一定要處理，重者則懲罰，但必須嚴格跟足程序。<br />\n<br />\n3. 事件性質嚴重，更應有好的機制，紀律委員會的集體決定肯定遠勝於學生輔導長的一人建議。<br />\n<br />\n4. 應盡快召開紀律委員會，不宜未審先判。<br />\n<br />\n5. 學生輔導長鄧裕南今次根據《學生紀律處理程序》第10.1條即時指令兩名學生停學，有關程序如下：<br />\n<br />\n[Student Disciplinary Procedures]<br />\n<br />\n10. Temporary Suspension of the right to use certain facility from the University<br />\n<br />\n10.1 The DSA, Panel, or the Student Affairs Committee may, where it is satisfied that a student being accused of a charge poses (a) a danger to the safety of other members of the University community or (b) an ongoing threat of disrupting the proper functioning of the University, temporarily suspend the student and/or deny the student's access to any facility or the whole campus, and/or other privileges and rights for which the student might otherwise be eligible until further notice.<br />\n<br />\n有關理據是，學生「要對學校成員的安全構成危險」或「對學校設施的中斷使用構成ongoing的威脅」，校方應清楚解釋理據。<br />\n<br />\n6. 學生輔導長鄧裕南在記者會上說，是根據視頻片段和教員口供來作為指令學生停學的依據，未知校方有否給與學生解釋的機會，令處理更公道？<br />\n<br />\n7\b. 無論最終如何處理，最重要是教返好學生，給他們改過的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n呢個鄧裕南夠膽死私下跳個程序，越權用10.1 迫學生停學，佢既理據話學生威脅都學校成員人身安全，如果係既話，點解冇人報警?呢個指控好嚴重，足以涉及刑事成份，如果你冇証據獨自攬權，咁你呢條友仔準備執定包伏，紀律委員會一但推翻你既決定，下一步就要追究你既責任，因你錯誤決定而對學生/學校構成既名譽等各項損失，你確定自己ready硬食晒???"},{"pid":"bdf2bd03c0146c62392b1d5ef73cc9f2517025de","tid":539653,"uid":36178,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"依家校方擺明就係監粗嚟"},{"pid":"e38b4842dab40ab4328fa4e3d7eac594fba46303","tid":539653,"uid":55375,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"仲係度講程序...佢唔跟你又會點呀"},{"pid":"216b23e5a810835b1af9c4281fcabc4f26a8e311","tid":539653,"uid":13724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e38b4842dab40ab4328fa4e3d7eac594fba46303","tid":539653,"uid":55375,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"仲係度講程序...佢唔跟你又會點呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:54:05.000Z","msg":"好似可以司法覆核"},{"pid":"98602900ba1fb6ebccabfd313fed9083bd8c5563","tid":539653,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"但政治上有計過<br />\n場撚屌喊戲真係呃到吓港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e2730bca622693360262bf746134a5feb44503","tid":539653,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98602900ba1fb6ebccabfd313fed9083bd8c5563","tid":539653,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"但政治上有計過<br />\n場撚屌喊戲真係呃到吓港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"一dd，要被昆個d點都會被昆<br />\n但有d人一見到呢類on9戲就會自然反應好反感<br />\n自動認定呢條友係契弟"},{"pid":"038f090ea65a9ebbc196f91f5ed994bb3e84e4d8","tid":539653,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"你覺得校方班契弟會理你呢啲程序仲同你解釋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f228a07ef0fe9c6ca41ce4663508a0f7c9322686","tid":539653,"uid":77257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲係度講程序